            <history-note id="DLM1076966"><amended-provision>Section 2(1)</amended-provision><emphasis style="bold">vehicle recovery service vehicle</emphasis>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM351797">section 4(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 77).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM1076968"><amended-provision>Section 2(1)</amended-provision><emphasis style="bold">work time</emphasis>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM351797">section 4(5)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 77).</history-note>
