            <history-note id="DLM434503"><amended-provision>Section 2(2)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>29 December 2001</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM128654">section 4(4)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport (Road Safety Enforcement) Amendment Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 104).</history-note>
