            <history-note id="DLM434891"><amended-provision>Section 83(1)(a)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>16 January 2006</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM352908">section 43(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 77).</history-note>
