            <history-note id="DLM2609792"><amended-provision>Section 96A(2)(a)(ii)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM2095545">section 23(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport (Enforcement Powers) Amendment Act 2009</amending-leg> (2009 No 36).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM2609794"><amended-provision>Section 96A(2A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM2095545">section 23(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport (Enforcement Powers) Amendment Act 2009</amending-leg> (2009 No 36).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM2609796"><amended-provision>Section 96A(4)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM2095545">section 23(4)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport (Enforcement Powers) Amendment Act 2009</amending-leg> (2009 No 36).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM2609798"><amended-provision>Section 96A first subsection (5)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM2095545">section 23(4)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport (Enforcement Powers) Amendment Act 2009</amending-leg> (2009 No 36).</history-note>
