            <history-note id="DLM435059"><amended-provision>Section 99(3)(c)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>16 January 2006</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM352936">section 53(6)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 77).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM435060"><amended-provision>Section 99(3)(d)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>18 September 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM205009">section 175(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Health Practitioners Competence Assurance Act 2003</amending-leg> (2003 No 48).</history-note>
