            <history-note id="DLM1079563"><amended-provision>Section 102(1)(b)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM352941">section 56(2)(b)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 77).</history-note>
